  "prompt": "Who is Disney's Princess Alice?",
  "response": "Disney's Princess Alice is a character based on Alice from Lewis Carroll's classic novel \"Alice's Adventures in Wonderland.\" While she is not an official Disney Princess like characters such as Cinderella or Belle, Alice is featured in Disney's animated adaptation of the story released in 1951, titled \"Alice in Wonderland.\" \n\nIn the film and various adaptations by Disney, Alice is portrayed as a curious and adventurous young girl who falls down a rabbit hole into a fantastical world filled with eccentric characters and surreal experiences. Though she doesn't fit the traditional mold of a Disney Princess, she remains a beloved character in Disney's lineup and is associated with themes of imagination and exploration.",
